hopobject.body: Sorry, you must have the wrong number isotretinoin 1 month Still, before you begin an exercise program, be sure to talk to your doctor about any risks with your pregnancy. The Mayo Clinic advises that for most pregnant women at least 30 minutes of moderate exercise is recommended on most days, and walking is a great exercise for beginners. Other good choices: swimming, low-impact aerobics, and cycling on a stationary bike.
